# ‚úàÔ∏è Autonomous Flight Price Tracker

This project monitors flight prices from **Porto (OPO)** to **S√£o Paulo - Guarulhos (GRU)** and sends an automatic email alert when the price drops to or below a specified target (e.g., ‚Ç¨400).

Built with **Node.js**, using the **Skyscanner API via RapidAPI**, and configured to run daily with a **cron job on Render**.

---

## ‚úÖ Features

-   Queries flight prices using the Skyscanner API
-   Checks 3 upcoming dates per run
-   Sends email alerts when the price is low enough
-   Runs automatically once a day (adjustable)

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

-   Node.js
-   Axios
-   Nodemailer
